{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aea6ce9970","title":"我们的决心：沈钧儒在社会主义自我改造促进大会上的开幕词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6a6c3943f3","index":0,"year":1958,"month":3,"day":16,"articleId":"aea6ce9970"}],"tags":[{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5d55e687a5","name":"沈钧儒"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4df23ca83f","type":"title","text":"我们的决心：沈钧儒在社会主义自我改造促进大会上的开幕词","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"8daa86bb36","type":"authors","text":"沈钧儒","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"7260fba4d9","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们！","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"1d317cffd4","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义自我改造促进大会开会了。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"903c311ef6","type":"paragraph","text":"参加今天大会的有各民主党派人士，无党派民主人士；有知识分子和工商界。我们万众一心，在首都天安门前，向毛主席、向共产党、向全国人民表示我们最大的决心。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"ff2116ff6e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们决心跟共产党走。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"7102415a73","type":"paragraph","text":"我们决心走社会主义道路。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"d8f32c0d4e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们决心向工农学习。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"25a0c32873","type":"paragraph","text":"我们决心改造自己——改造我们的政治立场和思想意识。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"916952e120","type":"paragraph","text":"我们决心把知识拿出来，把力量使出来，把心交出来，把一切都交出来，贡献给我们可爱的祖国，贡献给人民，贡献给党！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"cab3429e7d","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们！在祖国大跃进的新形势之下，我们的心在跳跃，我们的血在沸腾！","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"332d8b71ac","type":"paragraph","text":"首先让我们欢呼：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"1813b43608","type":"paragraph","text":"祖国万岁！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"d2dde2c179","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义万岁！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"14f1cc0eda","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党万岁！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"a47c9b28d5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席万岁！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"},{"id":"dac3666791","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《人民日报》1958年3月17日","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970"}],"page":{"id":"2c33345bc5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aea6ce9970","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}